{"tid":1772042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［12.8叉能廚］每人至少要搵1-2個616無去遊行既朋友去","createTime":"2019-12-06T09:51:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T11:13:51.000Z","uid":1971,"like":49,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"2fe2f5f4c08f03e8f3b4784eddf1f703ca3806dd","tid":1772042,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T09:51:54.000Z","msg":"連登仔一齊發揮你地既創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我要每人至少要拉多1,2個無去過既親戚朋友同事一齊去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別係二百萬人果次無去既盡量說服埋佢地一齊去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地要做既係走出同溫層 說服埋啲本身唔支持我地既人 <br />\n邀請佢出黎親眼見證下 幾百萬人係可以好齊心好團結咁表達訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今個星期日好大可能係香港歷史上最多人既一次遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n邀請佢地一同創造壯舉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同佢地講全地球🌍 世界每一個角落既媒體都會見到我地既身影<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n128行出黎 你就會成為時代週刊2019年世界最有影響力既人<br />\n128行出黎 你就會有機會成為諾貝爾和平獎得主之一<br />\n128行出黎 你就可以好自豪咁同後代講曾經參與過一件世界大事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n證明比世界睇 話比政權聽<br />\n香港人唔會放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n128 維園見</span></span>"},{"pid":"0df1ac6b067a197b85acaaa96d67bf4fddfc849e","tid":1772042,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T09:53:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"684fa8eaf8305a60f7595a47d14a93ffc304feac","tid":1772042,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T09:53:21.000Z","msg":"128 維園見"},{"pid":"5f2bc34f023d80bf6ffa057f1bd777112b06f429","tid":1772042,"uid":253978,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedB