ig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地要做既係走出同溫層 說服埋啲本身唔支持我地既人 <br />\n邀請佢出黎親眼見證下 幾百萬人係可以好齊心好團結咁表達訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今個星期日好大可能係香港歷史上最多人既一次遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n邀請佢地一同創造壯舉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同佢地講全地球🌍 世界每一個角落既媒體都會見到我地既身影<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n128行出黎 你就會成為時代週刊2019年世界最有影響力既人<br />\n128行出黎 你就會有機會成為諾貝爾和平獎得主之一<br />\n128行出黎 你就可以好自豪咁同後代講曾經參與過一件世界大事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n證明比世界睇 話比政權聽<br />\n香港人唔會放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n128 維園見</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T00:14:30.000Z","msg":"吹大雞！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f733a4231ebe6486a35af2c8fb2f286d31b88aa0","tid":1772042,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T02:27:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/big